Pull the code from git hub
Run mvn clean install
Run mvn assembly:assembly
Go to the target folder and unzip the twitterStreamServer.zip.
Go into the unzipped folder and run the below command
java -jar twitterStreamServer-1.0.jar

There is a property file in src/main/resources/twitterStream.properties which can be configured with the following values

consumerKey, consumerSecret, token, tokenSecret and  filters

filters can be a comma separated value from which the twitter will stream data to the server.

The other details can be found in the twitter app page.

There is a property file in src/main/resources/httpServer.properties which can be used to configured the http server port.


A Twitter Cli client can be downloaded from

    https://github.com/Ramkumar83/twitterCli